  <brief_title>Prospective Trial to Reduce Morbidity and Mortality After Lung Surgery in Patients With Reduced Pulmonary Capacity</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Randomized Controlled Trial to Reduce Morbidity and Mortality After Lung Surgery in Patients With FEV1 &lt; 70% of Expected Value or &lt; 1.5L</official_title>
