  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  resection of the lung

          -  FEV1 &lt;70% of expected value or below 1.5L

          -  18-80y

          -  given written informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  contraindication for epidural anesthesia

          -  prio ipsilateral thoracotomy

          -  chemotherapy &lt;6 weeks prior to study enter

          -  existing pneumonia (fever, elevated WCC, elevated CRP)
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
